2021年3月30日，[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]的[[阿爾斯特忠誠主義|阿爾斯特忠誠主義]]地區發生了一系列[[騷亂|騷亂]]和暴力示威<ref name="bbc-twelve-officers-injured-in-londonderry-disorder">{{Cite news|title=Twelve officers injured in Londonderry disorder|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-foyle-west-56626681|date=2021-04-03|access-date=2021-04-03|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409224705/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-foyle-west-56626681|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rte-petrol-bombs-and-masonry-thrown-at-police-in-derry">{{Cite news|title=Petrol bombs and masonry thrown at police in Derry|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/regional/2021/0402/1207651-derry-disturbances-latest/|date=2021-04-02|access-date=2021-04-03|publisher=RTÉ News and Current Affairs|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404191332/https://www.rte.ie/news/regional/2021/0402/1207651-derry-disturbances-latest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，示威地點主要發生在[[德里_(北愛爾蘭)|德里]]的{{en-link|水邊 (德里)|Waterside|水邊}}。在德里發生了四個晚上的騷亂之後，於4月2日蔓延到[[貝爾法斯特|貝爾法斯特]]南部，在那裡，[[阿爾斯特忠誠主義|阿爾斯特忠誠主義]]發起的抗議演變成一場涉及鐵棍、磚塊、磚石和汽油彈的暴力示威。此後，內亂於4月3日蔓延到[[紐敦阿比|紐敦阿比]]，那裡的汽車被劫持和燒毀，並且示威者還對警察使用了汽油彈<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|date=2021-04-04|title=Newtownabbey: Police attacked for second night in a row|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56631894|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407151926/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56631894|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月7日晚，北爱尔兰首府[[贝尔法斯特|贝尔法斯特]]再次发生骚乱。示威者向一辆正在行驶的公交车纵火，並朝警察投擲石块和汽油弹，导致7名警察受伤。此外示威者還與愛爾蘭人對峙，雙方互相投擲汽油彈。截至4月8日，騷亂導致至少50名警察受伤。10人被捕<ref name=東方網>{{cite news |title=民族矛盾与脱欧积怨爆发？北爱尔兰连日骚乱致50名警察受伤，有少年被捕 |url=http://news.yunnan.cn/system/2021/04/08/031382219.shtml |publisher=东方网·纵相新闻 |accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411124251/http://news.yunnan.cn/system/2021/04/08/031382219.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

騷亂的主要成因為親英派青年不滿[[英國脫歐協議|英國脫歐協議]]以及北爱尔兰政府宣布不起诉違反[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]防疫規定的[[新芬党|新芬党]]领导人<ref name=東方網/>。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Stroud_Street_Belfast_01.02.21.jpg|thumb]]

===爱尔兰海边界===
北爱尔兰[[阿爾斯特忠誠主義|忠诚派]]和[[愛爾蘭聯合主義|联合派]]认为[[北爱尔兰议定书|英国脱欧的贸易安排]]设立了屏障，将[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]和[[英国|英国]]其他地区分隔外<ref name=guardian-northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots/>。代表[[阿尔斯特志愿军|阿尔斯特志愿军]]和[[阿尔斯特防卫协会|阿尔斯特防卫协会]]等准军事组织的{{tsl|en|Loyalist Communities Council|忠诚派社群理事会}}宣布停止支持结束[[北爱尔兰问题|北爱尔兰问题]]的《[[贝尔法斯特协议|贝尔法斯特协议]]》，直至{{tsl|en|Irish Sea border|爱尔兰海边界}}被拆除<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-03-04|title=Loyalist group withdraws support for Good Friday Agreement|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56276653|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410105221/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56276653|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后，[[拉恩|拉恩]]一位码头工人收到匿名忠诚派准军事组织的死亡威胁，被迫带上家人离开<ref>{{Cite news|title=Larne Port worker and family relocated after loyalist threat|work=Belfast Telegraph|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/larne-port-worker-and-family-relocated-after-loyalist-threat-40260368.html|access-date=2021-04-05|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410103729/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/larne-port-worker-and-family-relocated-after-loyalist-threat-40260368.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===新芬党的葬礼===
事发前几周，当局宣布不起诉24名出席党内情报部长{{tsl|en|Bobby Storey|鲍比·斯托雷}}葬礼，吸引约2000人违反防疫规定到场观看<ref name=guardian-northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots/>的24名[[新芬黨|新芬黨]]党员<ref>{{Cite news|first=Kara|last=Fox|title=What's behind the recent violence in Northern Ireland?|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/04/09/uk/northern-ireland-violence-explainer-gbr-intl/index.html|access-date=2021-04-15|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414035844/https://www.cnn.com/2021/04/09/uk/northern-ireland-violence-explainer-gbr-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事后，[[北爱尔兰首席部长和副首席部长|北爱尔兰首席部长]][[阿琳·福斯特|阿琳·福斯特]]等联合派主要人物要求{{tsl|en|Police Service of Northern Ireland|北爱尔兰警察局}}局长{{tsl|en|Simon Byrne (police officer)|西蒙·伯恩}}辞职，认为他已经失去社区信任<ref name="guardian-northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots">{{Cite news|title=Northern Ireland's first minister joins calls for calm after Belfast riots|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/03/northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots|last=Blackall|first=Molly|date=2021-04-03|access-date=2021-04-03|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414192532/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/03/northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tj-psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast">{{Cite news|title=Teenagers aged 13 and 14 among eight arrests during rioting in loyalist area of south Belfast|url=https://www.thejournal.ie/psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast-5399929-Apr2021/|last1=McDermott|first1=Stephen|date=2021-04-03|access-date=2021-04-03|work=TheJournal.ie|last2=Duffy|first2=Rónán|agency=Press Association|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410103718/https://www.thejournal.ie/psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast-5399929-Apr2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。福斯特在推特表示：“民众普遍对警务工作失去信心，后果会马上出现<ref name=tj-psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast/>。”

===社会问题===
另外北爱尔兰警察局多次从阿尔斯特防卫协会旗下的{{tsl|en|UDA South East Antrim Brigade|UDA東南安特里姆旅}}中搜获非法毒品，极大程度上损坏警队形象<ref>{{Cite web|title=Northern Ireland riots 2021: why has there been violence in Belfast, Carrickfergus and Derry?|url=https://www.nationalworld.com/news/politics/northern-ireland-riots-2021-why-has-there-been-violence-in-belfast-carrickfergus-and-derry-3189607|access-date=2021-04-10|website=National World.|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410204324/https://www.nationalworld.com/news/politics/northern-ireland-riots-2021-why-has-there-been-violence-in-belfast-carrickfergus-and-derry-3189607|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Youth worker|青年工作者}}也认为[[青年会|青年会]]在疫情期间关闭，也是问题的根源之一<ref name="itvnews">{{cite news|url=https://www.itv.com/news/utv/2021-04-08/some-youth-services-to-resume-in-response-to-ni-unrest|title=Some youth services to resume in response to NI unrest|publisher=ITV News|date=2021-04-08|accessdate=2021-04-11|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411160749/https://www.itv.com/news/utv/2021-04-08/some-youth-services-to-resume-in-response-to-ni-unrest|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 骚乱过程 ==
===德里水边===
骚乱率先在联合派大本营Tullyalley庄园爆发<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56675894|title=Timeline: How Northern Ireland's violence unfolded|publisher=BBC News|first=Jordan|last=Kenny|date=2021-04-09|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408200430/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56675894|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rte-petrol-bombs-and-masonry-thrown-at-police-in-derry/>。当地的骚乱者和罗斯敦道/林肯法院（Rossdowny Road / Lincoln Court）地区的联合派主要使用汽油弹和砖头发动攻击<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/police-attacked-during-fourth-night-of-londonderry-disorder-40268505.html|title=Police attacked during fourth night of Londonderry disorder|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=David|last=Young|date=2021-04-02|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417122615/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/police-attacked-during-fourth-night-of-londonderry-disorder-40268505.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/crime-and-law/fears-mount-of-another-night-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-1.4527570|title=Fears mount of another night of violence in Northern Ireland|publisher=The Irish Times|date=2021-04-02|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410103719/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/crime-and-law/fears-mount-of-another-night-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-1.4527570|dead-url=no}}</ref>。纳尔逊大道（Nelson Drive）一家{{tsl|en|nursing home|疗养院}}遭到袭击，给里面的居民带来“巨大的恐惧和不安”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/care-home-damaged-and-officers-injured-after-fifth-night-of-derry-rioting-40271188.html|title=Care home damaged and officers injured after fifth night of Derry rioting|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=Eimear|last=McGovern|date=2021-04-03|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410103730/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/care-home-damaged-and-officers-injured-after-fifth-night-of-derry-rioting-40271188.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rte-petrol-bombs-and-masonry-thrown-at-police-in-derry/>有{{tsl|en|Backhoe loader|挖掘机}}的[[托盘|托盘]]被放下<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishmirror.ie/news/irish-news/violence-breaks-out-northern-ireland-23872601|title=Violence breaks out in Northern Ireland again as bus hijacked and set on fire and press photographer attacked|publisher=Irish Mirror|first=James|last=Ward|date=2021-04-07|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417122612/https://www.irishmirror.ie/news/irish-news/violence-breaks-out-northern-ireland-23872601|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/northern-ireland-bus-fire-belfast-b1828149.html|title=Northern Ireland riots: Bus hijacked and set on fire in Belfast|publisher=Independent|first=Sam|last=Hancock|date=2021-04-07|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407214516/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/northern-ireland-bus-fire-belfast-b1828149.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

当晚有12名警察受伤<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.sky.com/story/boy-13-among-arrests-after-15-police-officers-injured-in-belfast-riot-12264828|title=Northern Ireland: Cars set on fire in Newtownabbey spark fears of further trouble|publisher=Sky News|date=2021-04-04|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410132616/https://news.sky.com/story/boy-13-among-arrests-after-15-police-officers-injured-in-belfast-riot-12264828|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.ie/irish-news/unrest-in-northern-ireland-27police-officers-injured-as-riots-occur-in-belfast-and-derry-40273363.html|title=Unrest in Northern Ireland: 27 police officers injured as riots occur in Belfast and Derry|publisher=Irish Independent|first=Ciara|last=O'Loughlin|date=2021-04-04|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410132616/https://www.independent.ie/irish-news/unrest-in-northern-ireland-27police-officers-injured-as-riots-occur-in-belfast-and-derry-40273363.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月5日，20名年轻的滋事份子在斯珀林公园（Sperrin Park）焚烧汽车<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/violence-breaks-out-on-northern-ireland-streets-again-despite-appeals-for-calm-40279159.html|title=Violence breaks out on Northern Ireland streets again despite appeals for calm|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=James|last=Ward|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410131652/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/violence-breaks-out-on-northern-ireland-streets-again-despite-appeals-for-calm-40279159.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/05/further-violence-breaks-out-in-northern-ireland-despite-appeals-for-calm|title=Further violence breaks out in Northern Ireland despite appeals for calm|work=The Guardian|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410131650/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/05/further-violence-breaks-out-in-northern-ireland-despite-appeals-for-calm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===纽敦阿比===
4月3日晚，忠诚派所在的[[纽敦阿比|纽敦阿比]]奥尼尔路/多阿路（O'Neill Road / Doagh Road）地区爆发扰乱<ref name=tj-psni-unrest-newtownabbey-antrim>{{Cite news|title=PSNI respond to more unrest in loyalist areas of Co Antrim after cars hijacked and burnt out|url=https://www.thejournal.ie/psni-unrest-newtownabbey-antrim-5400451-Apr2021/|date=2021-04-04|access-date=2021-04-04|work=TheJournal.ie|agency=Press Association|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411095851/https://www.thejournal.ie/psni-unrest-newtownabbey-antrim-5400451-Apr2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方称遭到30枚汽油弹袭击，3辆汽车遭到挟持放火<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-04|title=Man charged with throwing petrol bomb after unrest in Newtownabbey|url=http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/04/northern-ireland-police-appeal-calm-cars-set-on-fire-newtownabbey|access-date=2021-04-05|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414192530/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/04/northern-ireland-police-appeal-calm-cars-set-on-fire-newtownabbey|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日爆发小规模骚乱，规模较前夜小<ref name=":0" />。

===卡里克弗格斯===
4月4日晚，阿尔斯特忠诚派在[[卡里克弗格斯|卡里克弗格斯]]北路（North Road）地区聚集，放火焚烧垃圾箱，将其推倒在地<ref>{{Cite news|title=Police attacked in further loyalist disturbances in Northern Ireland|language=en-GB|work=Belfast Telegraph|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/police-attacked-in-further-loyalist-disturbances-in-northern-ireland-40274996.html|access-date=2021-04-05|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411102658/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/police-attacked-in-further-loyalist-disturbances-in-northern-ireland-40274996.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方到场后，骚乱者出动砖块和汽油弹对抗，将对方逼出卡里克弗格斯庄园<ref>{{Cite web|title=Petrol bombs and bricks hurled at police in third night of violence in Northern Ireland|url=https://news.sky.com/story/petrol-bombs-and-bricks-hurled-at-police-in-third-night-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-12266306|access-date=2021-04-05|website=Sky News|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417122621/https://news.sky.com/story/petrol-bombs-and-bricks-hurled-at-police-in-third-night-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-12266306|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月5日，一群年轻人在北路地区聚集，在路中央放火<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thejournal.ie/loyalist-violence-northern-ireland-5400924-Apr2021/|title='Senseless and reckless': Police attacked as violence flares again in parts of Northern Ireland|publisher=TheJournal.ie, Press Association|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410134431/https://www.thejournal.ie/loyalist-violence-northern-ireland-5400924-Apr2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目击者称有零星的汽油弹飞向警方方向<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/police-attacked-in-further-loyalist-disturbances-in-northern-ireland-1106664.html|title=Police attacked in further loyalist disturbances in North|publisher=BreakingNews.ie|first=Rebecca|last=Black|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410134432/https://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/police-attacked-in-further-loyalist-disturbances-in-northern-ireland-1106664.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月7日，樱桃步道（Cherry Walk）和格伦菲尔德步道（Glenfield Walk）有民居玻璃被砸，居民迅速逃离，松林大道（Pinewood Avenue）一名养老金领取者的家被攻击。被针对的目标被指与当局勾结。[[阿尔斯特志愿军|阿尔斯特志愿军]]称一场“21世纪的种族清洗”正在进行，下令驱逐住在一处房屋的所有天主教家庭<ref name=belfast-telegraph-uvf-orders-removal-of-catholic-families-from-carrickfergus>{{Cite news|title=UVF orders removal of Catholic families from Carrickfergus housing estate in '21st century form of ethnic cleansing'|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sunday-life/news/uvf-orders-removal-of-catholic-families-from-carrickfergus-housing-estate-in-21st-century-form-of-ethnic-cleansing-40297946.html|last=Lee|first=John|date=2021-04-11|access-date=2021-04-12|work=Belfast Telegraph|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412143808/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sunday-life/news/uvf-orders-removal-of-catholic-families-from-carrickfergus-housing-estate-in-21st-century-form-of-ethnic-cleansing-40297946.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===非法游行===
4月5日，忠诚派在{{tsl|en|Portadown|波塔当}}、[[巴利米納|巴利米納]]和{{tsl|en|Markethill|马特希尔}}等地举行非法游行，部分参加者佩戴口罩<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishnews.com/news/northernirelandnews/2021/04/07/news/illegal-loyalist-parade-in-ballymena-sparks-riot-with-more-marches-expected-2279657/|title=Illegal loyalist parade in Ballymena sparks riot, with more marches expected|publisher=The Irish News|first=Claire|last=Simpson|date=2021-04-07|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410135204/https://www.irishnews.com/news/northernirelandnews/2021/04/07/news/illegal-loyalist-parade-in-ballymena-sparks-riot-with-more-marches-expected-2279657/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.armaghi.com/news/portadown-news/appeal-for-calm-as-masked-loyalists-parade-through-streets-of-portadown/131704|title=Appeal for calm as 'masked loyalists parade through streets of Portadown'|website=Armaghi|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410135204/https://www.armaghi.com/news/portadown-news/appeal-for-calm-as-masked-loyalists-parade-through-streets-of-portadown/131704|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56646392|title=PSNI say 41 officers injured during NI rioting|publisher=BBC News|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410135202/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56646392|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当地警方正调查这些未告知游行委员会的游行<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/2021/0405/1207947-loyalist-violence-police/|title=Fresh trouble in Northern Ireland despite appeals for calm|publisher=RTÉ News and Current Affairs|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410135202/https://www.rte.ie/news/2021/0405/1207947-loyalist-violence-police/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===贝尔法斯特===
[[File:Sandy_Row_banner_March_2021.jpg|thumb]]
4月2日，[[贝尔法斯特|贝尔法斯特]]南部{{tsl|en|Sandy Row|桑迪街}}地区爆发骚乱<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/020421-sandy-row-riot/|title=Appeal for calm after officers injured in Sandy Row riot|website=Police Service of Northern Ireland|date=2021-04-02|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410133705/https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/020421-sandy-row-riot/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抗议活动过后，忠诚派示威者与警方爆发冲突，投掷玻璃瓶、砖块、汽油弹和焰火<ref name="#1">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56623901|title=Sandy Row riot: Leaders appeal for calm after Belfast riot|publisher=BBC News|date=2021-04-02|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410133703/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56623901|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8名示威者被捕，包括一名13岁的男孩，被捕者年龄为13岁至25岁<ref name="#1"/>。

4月7日，忠诚派青年在贝尔法斯特拉纳克路（Lanark Way）和{{tsl|en|Shankill Road|香吉路}}交汇处胁持一辆公交车并纵火<ref name=tj-bus-hijacked-and-set-on-fire-in-west-belfast-after-days-of-violence-in-northern-ireland>{{Cite news|title=Widespread condemnation after bus hijacked and set on fire in Belfast|url=https://www.thejournal.ie/bus-hijacked-and-set-on-fire-in-west-belfast-after-days-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-5403241-Apr2021/|agency=Press Association|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411103841/https://www.thejournal.ie/bus-hijacked-and-set-on-fire-in-west-belfast-after-days-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-5403241-Apr2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rte-bus-petrol-bombed-in-further-belfast-violence>{{Cite news|title=Bus petrol-bombed in further Belfast violence|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/ireland/2021/0407/1208499-northern-ireland/|last=Kearney|first=Vincent|date=2021-04-07|access-date=2021-04-08|publisher=RTÉ News|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411000533/https://www.rte.ie/news/ireland/2021/0407/1208499-northern-ireland/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/gallery/2021/4/8/belfast-protesters-hijack-bus-attack-police-as-violence-continue|title=Belfast protesters set fire to hijacked bus as violence continues|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2021-04-08|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414234732/https://www.aljazeera.com/gallery/2021/4/8/belfast-protesters-hijack-bus-attack-police-as-violence-continue|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Belfast Telegraph|贝尔法斯特电讯报}}》一名摄影师被袭击，相机被毁<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/belfast/attack-on-belfast-telegraph-photographer-kevin-scott-condemned-40286493.html|title=Attack on Belfast Telegraph photographer Kevin Scott condemned|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=Gareth|last=Cross|date=2021-04-08|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410142206/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/belfast/attack-on-belfast-telegraph-photographer-kevin-scott-condemned-40286493.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|peace lines|和平分界线}}两旁的示威者互相投掷汽油弹<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/04/07/belfast-violence-petrol-bomb-thrown-onto-bus-northern-ireland/|title=Boris Johnson condemns Belfast violence after petrol bomb thrown onto bus|first=Telegraph|last=Reporters|date=2021-04-07|via=Telegraph|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411103841/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/04/07/belfast-violence-petrol-bomb-thrown-onto-bus-northern-ireland/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thejournal.ie/bus-hijacked-and-set-on-fire-in-west-belfast-after-days-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-5403241-Apr2021/|title=Peace wall violence in Belfast 'at a scale we have not seen in recent years'|publisher=TheJournal|first1=Stephen|last1=McDermott|first2=Rónán|last2=Duffy|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411103841/https://www.thejournal.ie/bus-hijacked-and-set-on-fire-in-west-belfast-after-days-of-violence-in-northern-ireland-5403241-Apr2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月8日，贝尔法斯特西部再度有示威者聚集，在[[愛爾蘭民族主義|民族主义]]地区{{tsl|en|Springfield Road|春田路}}附近向警方投掷砖块、汽油弹等物品<ref>{{Cite news|title=Northern Ireland riots: Youths clash with police in second night of trouble in west Belfast|language=en-GB|work=belfasttelegraph|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/youths-clash-with-police-in-second-night-of-trouble-in-west-belfast-40290117.html|access-date=2021-04-08|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417122642/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/belfast/video-youths-clash-with-police-in-second-night-of-trouble-in-west-belfast-40290117.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方6年来首次在当地以[[水炮|水炮]]回应<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/water-cannon-used-in-northern-ireland-for-first-time-in-six-years-40292693.html|title=Water cannon used in Northern Ireland for first time in six years|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=Christopher|last=Leebody|date=2021-04-09|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412140520/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/water-cannon-used-in-northern-ireland-for-first-time-in-six-years-40292693.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/ulster/2021/0408/1208702-northern-ireland-violence/|title=Water cannon deployed during rioting in Belfast|publisher=RTÉ News and Current Affairs|date=2021-04-09|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414072332/https://www.rte.ie/news/ulster/2021/0408/1208702-northern-ireland-violence/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thejournal.ie/taoiseach-prime-minister-meeting-northern-ireland-5404221-Apr2021/|title=Police blast rioters with water cannon as violence flares again in Northern Ireland|publisher=TheJournal.ie|first=Orla|last=Dwyer|date=2021-04-09|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410142209/https://www.thejournal.ie/taoiseach-prime-minister-meeting-northern-ireland-5404221-Apr2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。19名警察和1头[[警犬|警犬]]受伤<ref>{{Cite news|title=Northern Ireland riots: Police dog injured along with 19 officers, as MLA questions PSNI tactics in Belfast disorder|language=en-GB|work=belfasttelegraph|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/belfast/police-dog-injured-along-with-19-officers-as-mla-questions-psni-belfast-disorder-tactics-40292004.html|access-date=2021-04-09|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409120402/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/belfast/police-dog-injured-along-with-19-officers-as-mla-questions-psni-belfast-disorder-tactics-40292004.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

4月9日，骚乱最后一天，忠诚派领袖敦促社群停止一切示威活动，尊重当天[[愛丁堡公爵菲臘親王之死|病故]]的[[爱丁堡公爵菲利普亲王|爱丁堡公爵菲利普亲王]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfastlive.co.uk/news/belfast-news/belfast-riots-calls-planned-protests-20352507|title=Belfast riots: Calls for planned protests to be cancelled in wake of Prince Philip's death|publisher=Belfast Live|first=Sarah|last=Scott|date=2021-04-09|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410142217/https://www.belfastlive.co.uk/news/belfast-news/belfast-riots-calls-planned-protests-20352507|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/fears-that-violence-in-northern-ireland-could-continue-over-weekend-1109222.html|title=Pockets of unrest flare up in North despite call for calm after royal death|publisher=BreakingNews.ie|first=James|last=Ward|date=2021-04-10|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410142209/https://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/fears-that-violence-in-northern-ireland-could-continue-over-weekend-1109222.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/crime-and-law/north-teenagers-arrested-as-number-of-psni-officers-injured-in-unrest-reaches-88-1.4534197|title=North: Teenagers arrested as number of PSNI officers injured in unrest reaches 88|publisher=The Irish Times|date=2021-04-10|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410142207/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/crime-and-law/north-teenagers-arrested-as-number-of-psni-officers-injured-in-unrest-reaches-88-1.4534197|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而贝尔法斯特北部虎湾地区再度有警民冲突，警方遭遇石头和玻璃瓶攻击，一辆汽车被纵火<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/psni-attacked-and-car-set-ablaze-in-loyalist-tiger-s-bay-area-of-belfast-1.4533461|title=PSNI attacked and car set ablaze in loyalist Tiger's Bay area of Belfast|publisher=The Irish Times|date=2021-04-10|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410142207/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/psni-attacked-and-car-set-ablaze-in-loyalist-tiger-s-bay-area-of-belfast-1.4533461|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Northern Ireland riots: Disorder enters eighth night as police attacked in Belfast|language=en-GB|work=belfasttelegraph|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/disorder-enters-eighth-night-as-police-attacked-in-belfast-40295775.html|access-date=2021-04-10|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413010311/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/disorder-enters-eighth-night-as-police-attacked-in-belfast-40295775.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方确认有14名警员受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/100421-14-officers-injured-in-latest-belfast-disorder/|title=14 officers injured in latest Belfast disorder|website=Police Service of Northern Ireland|date=2021-04-09|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410162652/https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/100421-14-officers-injured-in-latest-belfast-disorder/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56699716|title=NI riots: Fourteen more police officers injured in night of violence|publisher=BBC News|date=2021-04-10|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411230407/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56699716|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/2021/0410/1208944-northern-ireland/|title=14 PSNI officers injured in violent protests|publisher=RTÉ News and Current Affairs|date=2021-04-10|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410160139/https://www.rte.ie/news/2021/0410/1208944-northern-ireland/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[科尔雷因|科尔雷因]]，部分蒙面青少年设置纵火路障，向警方投掷汽油弹<ref>{{cite news |title=Timeline: How Northern Ireland's violence unfolded |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56675894 |agency=BBC |date=2021-04-12 |accessdate=2021-04-17 |archive-date=2021-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408200430/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56675894 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

