德里市和斯特拉班地区总指挥官、[[总警司|总警司]]达林·琼斯（Darrin Jones）谴责暴动行径，指“完全不可接受”。他在声明中表示：
{{quote|对于我们这个社会最弱势的一群人来说，养老院应该是避风港。我想亲自对昨天参与骚乱的人士说，如果你的祖父母住在这间养老院，成为这次暴力行动的目标，你会怎么想？德里/伦敦德里地区的骚乱已经连续发生五个夜晚了，情况完全不可接受。很明显，我们都想对参与人士说这样的行为无法容忍。德里/伦敦德里地区的人民理应安全地留在家中，走在街上也不至于感到害怕。我想对那些在社区中有影响的人们——不管是父母、监护人、社区代表还是民选代表说——请利用你的影响力，防止年轻人被卷入犯罪行为，让他们确保人声安全，远离一切危险。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/030421-update-on-derrylondonderry-disorder/|title=Update on Derry/Londonderry disorder|publisher=Police Service of Northern Ireland|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410170610/https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/030421-update-on-derrylondonderry-disorder/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bbc-twelve-officers-injured-in-londonderry-disorder/><ref name=rte-petrol-bombs-and-masonry-thrown-at-police-in-derry/>}}

4月2日，贝尔法斯特地区[[总警司|总警司]]西蒙·瓦尔斯（Simon Walls）指当地的抗议活动迅速演变成针对警方的袭击<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/030421-update-on-belfast-disorder32/|title=Update on Belfast disorder|website=Police Service of Northern Ireland|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410171342/https://www.psni.police.uk/news/Latest-News/030421-update-on-belfast-disorder32/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，他称看到13、14岁的儿童被捕，今天早上关在{{tsl|en|custody suite|监护套房}}，面临调查和可能的罪名，“觉得痛心”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/eight-arrested-and-15-officers-injured-after-belfast-riot-40271144.html|title=Eight arrested and 15 officers injured after Belfast riot|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=Michelle|last=Devane|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410171341/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/eight-arrested-and-15-officers-injured-after-belfast-riot-40271144.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他恳求有影响力的人士阻止有暴力意向的人士，和平地解决紧张局面及争端<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.newstalk.com/news/eight-police-officers-injured-following-riots-in-south-belfast-1174608|title=Eight police officers injured following riots in south Belfast|publisher=Newstalk|first=Marita|last=Moloney|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410171343/https://www.newstalk.com/news/eight-police-officers-injured-following-riots-in-south-belfast-1174608|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

总警司大卫·贝克（Davy Beck）于4月5日下午指警方已准备好应付升级的暴动行为，但也敦促社区领袖防止克劳弗恩和纽敦阿比/卡里克弗格斯地区连续三个晚上出现暴动。他认为有一小撮感到不满的犯罪分子鼓动年轻人参与骚乱<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishnews.com/news/northernirelandnews/2021/04/06/news/heavy-police-patrols-after-third-consecutive-night-of-senseless-and-reckless-violence-2278807/|work=Irish News|title=Heavy police patrols after third consecutive night of 'senseless and reckless' violence|author=Claire Simpson|date=2021-04-06|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406082409/https://www.irishnews.com/news/northernirelandnews/2021/04/06/news/heavy-police-patrols-after-third-consecutive-night-of-senseless-and-reckless-violence-2278807/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

助理首席警官乔纳森·罗伯茨（Jonathan Roberts）称4月7日的暴力事件是北爱尔兰多年来最严重的骚乱<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56664868|title=Belfast: Rioting 'was worst seen in Northern Ireland in years'|date=2021-04-08|work=BBC News|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410104556/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56664868|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===地方官员===
斯托蒙特{{tsl|en|Department of Justice (Northern Ireland)|北爱尔兰司法部|司法部长}}兼[[北爱尔兰联盟党|联盟党]]党魁[[内奥米·郎|内奥米·郎]]认为政治领袖的言辞带来骚乱的严重后果，表示扰乱对谁都没有好，不管是上前线应对的警察，还是大多数赌上未来参与其中的年轻人<ref name=tj-psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast/>。他呼吁领导人必须作出“负责任的表现，在最近几天降低煽动性言论”<ref name=tj-psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast/>。

首席部长阿琳·福斯特批评示威者，呼吁年轻人“不要加入骚乱”，指暴力行为无助于局面改善<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/03/northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots|title=Northern Ireland’s first minister joins calls for calm after Belfast riots|publisher=The Guardian|first=Molly|last=Blackall|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-03|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414192532/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/03/northern-ireland-secretary-calls-for-calm-after-belfast-riots|dead-url=no}}</ref>，呼吁父母尽量管好孩子<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/stormont-first-minister-appeals-for-calm-following-belfast-rioting-40271027.html|title=Stormont First Minister appeals for calm following Belfast rioting|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|first=Michelle|last=Devane|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410172055/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/stormont-first-minister-appeals-for-calm-following-belfast-rioting-40271027.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

新芬党方面，议员{{tsl|en|Paul Maskey|保罗·马斯基}}认为年轻人“被不法分子利用”，认为[[民主统一党_(北爱尔兰)|民主统一党]]是局面紧张的罪魁祸首<ref name=tj-psni-injured-rioting-sandy-row-belfast/>。{{tsl|en|Member of the Legislative Assembly (Northern Ireland)|北爱尔兰立法议会议员}}{{tsl|en|Gerry Kelly|格里·凯利}}是警务委员会委员，他指责联合派领袖煽动暴力，尤其是民主统一党<ref name=bbc-sinister-elements-getting-younger-people-to-attack-psni>{{Cite news|title='Sinister elements' getting younger people to attack PSNI|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56634052|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-05|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410051700/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-56634052|dead-url=no}}</ref>。北爱议员{{tsl|en|John O'Dowd|约翰·奥多德}}谴责波顿镇的非法集会，认为活动由一群蒙面份子煽动当地社区挑起。[[阿爾斯特統一黨|阿爾斯特統一黨]]北爱议员{{tsl|en|Doug Beattie|道格·比蒂}}认为大家都负有责任<ref name=bbc-sinister-elements-getting-younger-people-to-attack-psni/>。

{{tsl|en|Derry City and Strabane District Council|德里市和斯特拉班区议会}}民主统一党籍议员认为，这次暴动看起来很让人压抑：“我在水边与年轻人一起工作了很多年。我从未见过像这样的愤怒<ref name=bbc-twelve-officers-injured-in-londonderry-disorder/>”。

4月8日，{{tsl|en|Department of Education (Northern Ireland)|北爱尔兰教育部|北爱尔兰教育部长}}{{tsl|en|Peter Weir (politician)|彼得·威尔}}宣布重新开放局势紧张地区的青年设施，防止年轻人陷入麻烦。这些机构在疫情封城期间被关闭<ref name="itvnews"/>。

== 各界反应 ==
[[爱尔兰总理|爱尔兰总理]][[邁克·馬丁|邁克·馬丁]]、[[英国首相|英国首相]][[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]和[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]谴责暴力行为，表达对当地局势的关注，呼吁各方冷静<ref>{{Cite news|last1=O'Carroll|first1=Lisa|last2=Carroll|first2=Rory|last3=Syal|first3=Rajeev|date=2021-04-08|title=White House expresses concern over Northern Ireland violence|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/08/white-house-joe-biden-expresses-concern-over-northern-ireland-violence|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414003814/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/08/white-house-joe-biden-expresses-concern-over-northern-ireland-violence|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Leahy|first1=Pat|last2=Suzanne|first2=Lynch|last3=Hutton|first3=Brian|date=2021-04-08|title=Taoiseach, Boris Johnson and Joe Biden urge calm following Northern Ireland riots|work=The Irish Times|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/taoiseach-boris-johnson-and-joe-biden-urge-calm-following-northern-ireland-riots-1.4532102|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409233805/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/taoiseach-boris-johnson-and-joe-biden-urge-calm-following-northern-ireland-riots-1.4532102|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]暂停对英国的法律行为。此前，英国单方面扩大大不列颠地区进入北爱尔兰地区货物的检查豁免范围<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-04-09/eu-to-delay-brexit-legal-action-amid-northern-ireland-violence|title=EU to Delay Brexit Legal Action Amid Northern Ireland Violence|date=2021-04-09|work=Bloomberg|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414115837/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-04-09/eu-to-delay-brexit-legal-action-amid-northern-ireland-violence|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

与民主统一党关系密切的南贝尔法斯特{{tsl|en|Ulster Political Research Group|阿尔斯特政治研究小组}}是首个于4月8日呼吁结束骚乱的忠诚派团体。团体指“最近的乱局完全偏偏离引起我们社区沮丧和不满的原始问题，政治手段比街头暴力更适合解决问题<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/newsletters/belfast-beat/south-belfast-uprg-becomes-first-loyalist-group-to-call-for-an-end-to-unrest-40288752.html|title=South Belfast UPRG becomes first loyalist group to call for an end to unrest|first=Allison|last=Morris|date=2021-04-08|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413020628/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/newsletters/belfast-beat/south-belfast-uprg-becomes-first-loyalist-group-to-call-for-an-end-to-unrest-40288752.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”忠诚派社区理事会4月9日发表声明，指未有证据显示下辖组织直接或间接参与近日的暴力行动。他们呼吁外界应和平地对忠诚派社群采取行动，也希望政府出面斡旋新协议，确保北爱尔兰与英国其他地区，以及爱尔兰岛内部没有硬边界<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.belfastlive.co.uk/news/belfast-news/belfast-riots-loyalist-communities-council-20351387|title=Belfast riots: Loyalist Communities Council issue statement after days of violence|first=Sarah|last=Scott|date=2021-04-09|publisher=Belfast Live|accessdate=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414004253/https://www.belfastlive.co.uk/news/belfast-news/belfast-riots-loyalist-communities-council-20351387|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

